title: Upfront
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Reportedly offers fish in addition to a veg menu. Restaurant and coffee shop. Salads, sandwiches, quiche, coffees, teas, cakes, desserts. Gluten free options. Tables are available in the main gallery, the conservatory space and on the outside patio. Also has a gallery and a puppet theater which stages shows at Christmas, Easter, and in the summer.
